obj_root_law_sections_15_content:
  string
  line `[Amendment of Act 52 of 1974.] Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 2001 (30 of 2001), s. 2`
  line `and the First Schedule (w.e.f.3-9-2001).`
obj_root_law_sections_15_footnotes:
